name: The Backrooms v1.3
description:
Welcome to the Backrooms, an endless liminal space with only the madness of mono-yellow and the noise of fluorescent lights at maximum hum-buzz to keep you company. God save you if you hear something nearby, because it sure as hell has heard you.

WASD to move
L for flashlight...you'll need it.
Space to jump.

Check the walls.
